& [InferenceJobResult] is controlled explosion readiness inference
  + [focus] is determining readiness for SOP expansion
  + [inside] is the high-energy idea's atomic_thought and spark that trigger potential controlled explosion
  + [boundary] is the ControlledExplosionReadiness framework, compression pressure, and governor checks limiting expansion
  + [outside] is unresolved evidence gaps, scope creep, or conflicting governance that must be vented
  + [inference] is ready for controlled expansion only if spark aligns with governor and all compression constraints are satisfied
  + [caution] is maintain evidence, balance, security, and avoid expanding without piston coupling to useful output
  + [next_step] is document the inference, propose a controlled_explosion plan, and schedule review of exhaust items
